@Tatemo wrote:

I coded noobscape for 2 years and yes it was my first source. Tbh it’s not actually that nice horrible conventions and a lot of unnessary code. Tasham scape and Zombiescape are pretty good. Cleaned Czar is the best though. Or maybe project covic. If you want an example of what good code looks like look at the animator code in project covic. I made that and it’s about the most perfect in you can get imo.

If you tried and spent time on it I am sure you could make a source better than noobscape. It’s all about dedication to coding. I never released a source before Noobscape because they weren’t really good enough or anything new I recommend that more people on mopar think before they release.
